<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato');
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora');

    main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      /* align horizontal */
      align-items: center;
      /* align vertical */
      background-color: #f5efe9;
    }

    .logo {
      margin: 30px auto;
    }

    section {
      background-color: white;
      width: 540px;
      padding-top: 35px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .title {
      font-family: 'Lora';
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: normal;
      color: #41413a;
      margin: auto 77px;
    }

    .content {
      margin: 41px 50px;
      font-family: 'Lato';
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 30px;
      text-align: left;
      color: #7b776c;
    }

    a.go {
      display:block;
      text-align:center;
      margin: 35px 25px 0 25px;
      padding: 23px 50px 23px 50px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      background-color: #924623;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    footer {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: row;
      margin: 35px auto;
      font-family: 'Lato';
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #7b776c;
    }

    a.facebook {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #7b776c;
      line-height: 22px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/EmailMessage"
  style="-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-text-size-adjust: none; width: 100% !important; height: 100%; line-height: 1.6em; background-color: white; margin: 0;"
  bgcolor="white">
  <main>
    <div class='logo'>
      <a href="http://www.remoteshiva.org">
        <img src="https://remoteshiva-assets.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/logo%402x.png" width="229px" height='37px'
          alt="logo" border="0" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <section>
      <div class='title'>Welcome to RemoteShiva</div>
      <div class='content'>
        Dear {{organizerName}},
        <br /><br />
        Thanks for making an account with RemoteShiva. We know that organizing a shiva is a sensitive and
        complex process, and we hope we can make it a bit easier for you and the mourners you’re supporting.
        <p style='margin-bottom: 35px;'>
          Now that you’ve created an account, finish setting up the shiva page if you haven’t done so already. If you get stuck during the process, take a look at our <a href="https://blog.remoteshiva.org/index.php/faq/">help site</a> to find answers to common questions.
        </p>
        <p style='margin-bottom: 35px;'>
          Once you’ve set up the shiva page, we recommend having one of the mourners take a quick look at it to make sure
          they’re comfortable with the information being shared.</p>
        <p style='margin-bottom: 35px;'>
          Then share the link to the shiva page with all the friends and relatives of the mourners who are seeking information about the shiva.
        </p>
        <p style='margin-bottom: 35px;'>
          We hope our platform helps make a difficult time a bit easier for you to coordinate during this difficult time.
        </p>
        <p style='margin-bottom: 35px;'>
          Warmly,<br />
          The RemoteShiva Volunteer Team
        </p>
        <a href='{{dashboardUrl}}' class='go'>Go to RemoteShiva</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!--<section>
      <div class='content'>
        <div class='title'>
          Send a meal
        </div>
        <p>The mourners are also accepting meal deliveries. To sign up for a slot to deliver food, click here.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section>
      <div class='content'>
        <div class='title'>
          Memorial donations
        </div>
        <p>
          If you’d like to make a donation in [name of deceased]’s honor, the mourners suggest donationlink.com.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>-->
    <footer>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/remoteshiva" class='facebook'>
        <img src="https://remoteshiva-assets.s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/facebook-gray-transparent.png" width="20px"
          height="20px" alt="fb" />
        <span>Follow us on Facebook</span>
      </a>

    </footer>
  </main>
</body>

</html>
